Chris Holmes

About

Hi! Im Chris Holmes, Head of Data and Analytics at Full Fibre Ltd in the South West of England.

Im a professional, confident and highly driven problem solver with a keen eye for scientific rigour and reproducible analysis.

I have a particular love for the R programming language and enjoy contributing to the R open source community through the development of tools and packages (most often related to data visualisation).

I am also a Nintendo and Columbo enthusiast!

Education

  • PhD in Physics - University of Exeter, UK
  • 1st Class Masters Degree in Physics - University of Exeter, UK

Professional Experience

  • Full Fibre Ltd - Head of Data and Analytics - [Sep 2023 - Present]
  • Full Fibre Ltd - Data Scientist - [Aug 2021 - Sep 2023]
  • Openreach Ltd (BT) - Senior Data Scientist - [Apr 2017 - Aug 2021]
  • Openreach Ltd (BT) - Data Scientist - [Sep 2015 - Apr 2017]
  • Imerys Minerals Ltd - Research Scientist - [Nov 2011 - Aug 2015]
